title.description: A short, summary of the problem type. Written in english and readable for engineers (usually not suited for non technical stakeholders and not localized)

status.description: The HTTP status code generated by the origin server for this occurrence of the problem.

detail.description: A human-readable explanation specific to this occurrence of the problem.

cityParam.name: city
cityParam.description: City is used to define a geo point that will be used as a CENTER for a search.

zipParam.name: zip
zipParam.description: ZIP is used to define a geo point that will be used as a CENTER for a search.

streetParam.name: street
streetParam.description: Street is used to define a geo point that will be used as a CENTER for a search. Parameter is optional.

countryParam.name: country
countryParam.description: Country is used to define a geo point that will be used as a CENTER for a search.

latParam.name: lat
latParam.description: Latitude of a point that will be used as a center of the search.

orgaDataParam.name: orgaData
orgaDataParam.description: If true, response includes all organizational units which are referenced in a branch.

lngParam.name: lng
lngParam.description: Longitude of a point that will be used as a center of the search.

typeParam.name: type
typeParam.description: Aggregate branches based on a given TYPE.

approxDistanceParam.name: approxDistance
approxDistanceParam.description: Compute and display approximate distance if true.

minBranchesParam.name: minBranches
minBranchesParam.description: Minimum number of results. If there are not enough branches within the original search radius, the remaining results will come from beyond the initial search area.

accuracyParam.name: accuracy
accuracyParam.description: The accuracy of the search area. Value is defined in KM. Maximum 500.

advisorsParam.name: advisors
advisorsParam.description: When set to true, only branches with advisors will be displayed. If false, only those without advisors are displayed.

filtersParam.name: filters
filtersParam.description: Array of values, determining what sort of information to retrieve.

API Key Authentication.name: KeyId
API Key Authentication.description: API key authentication using an API key without additional secret.
